<div id="ccc-address-checker" class="mt-4"></div>
<div id="ccc-verified-content" class="address available mt-2" style="display: none;">
	<h3>Woohoo! We're <span class="highlight">deploying in your area.</span></h3>
	<p>Take a look at our plans and see what's right for you.</p> 
	<p><a href="
		{%- if availabilityCheckerLink %}
			{{ availabilityCheckerLink }}
		{%- else %}
		#start
		{%- endif %}
		" class="button">See plans</a></p> 
</div>
<div id="ccc-warning-content" class="address error mt-2" style="display: none;">
	<p></p> 
</div>
<div id="ccc-unverified-content" class="address unavailable mt-2" style="display: none;">
	<h3>Bugger! We’re <span class="highlight">not there yet 🙁</span></h3>
	<p>We’re not in your area yet, but we’re on our way.</p> 
	<p>Be the first to know when it's available.</p> 
	<p><a href="/waitlist/" class="button">Join the waitlist</a></p> 
</div>